msgid "Status details are available only when the NetBird service is running. See the Authentication tab to enable, start, or log in."
msgstr "仅当 NetBird 服务运行时才显示状态详情。请前往认证标签页以启用、启动或登录。"

msgid "The NetBird binary was not found. Install the netbird package, then return here."
msgstr "未找到 NetBird 二进制文件。请先安装 netbird 软件包，然后返回此页面。"

msgid "The NetBird service is installed and enabled but not running."
msgstr "NetBird 服务已安装并启用，但未在运行。"

