msgstr "%s 软件包为保底版本；最新官方版功能更完整。"

msgid "The current session is disconnected, but your login identity is kept. Click Connect below to reconnect; no setup key is needed."
msgstr "已断开当前连接，登录身份仍保留。点下方「连接」重连，无需安装密钥。"

msgid "Not connected to the server. Enter the management URL and key below to connect."
msgstr "未连接服务端。请在下方输入管理 URL 与密钥进行连接。"

msgid "This will deregister this device and remove the local NetBird identity. You will need a setup key to log in again. This is different from \"Disconnect\", which keeps your credentials."
msgstr "此操作将注销本设备并删除本地 NetBird 身份。再次登录需要安装密钥。这与\"断开连接\"不同，断开连接会保留凭据。"

